This script will validate the users IP so the user is able to use your script.
You can also let users add their own IP address to the Valid List by letting them mail
the activation link to a range of valid email addresses or domains.

With this script you can give customers access to what ever you want.

Add the domains you want to be valid;
Add email addresses you want to be valid;
Go to : http://YOURDOMAIN.COM/?add_ip=1

Just put 11 lines in your index.php

Written by Theo van der Sluijs with MongoDB
http://www.vandersluijs.nl
http://www.itheo.nl
